---
title: Easy Breezy Veggie Burrito Bowl   with spiced beans, avocado salsa and creme fraiche
description: Burrito bowls as a dinner idea are always exciting—a fiesta of flavours just waiting to happen. This veggie version is filled with Mexican spiced beans, a vibrant avocado salsa and creme fraiche to cool down. All this sits atop a generous helping of fluffy garlic rice.
